Name of Post:

Uttar Pradesh UPSESSB Trained Graduate Teacher UP TGT Online Form 2022 for 3539 Post
Post Date / Update: 17 June 2022 | 11:30 AM
Short Information : Uttar Pradesh Secondary Education Service Selection Board (UPSESSB) has released the notification of Trained Graduate Teacher TGT Teacher Recruitment for 3539 posts. Those who are interested in this recruitment and fulfill the eligibility can apply online from 09 June 2022 to 03 July 2022. For the information of eligibility, age limit, selection procedure, pay scale, syllabus in recruitment, read the up tgt 2022 notification and then apply.

  • Pay Exam Fee Last Date: 13/07/2022 Extended
  • Complete Form Last Date : 16/07/2022 Extended
  • Exam Date: Notified Soon
  • Admit Card Available : Before Exam

Application Fee

  • General / OBC : 750/-
  • EWS / : 450/-
  • SC : 450/-
  • ST : 250/-
  • Pay the Examination Fee Through Debit Card / Credit Card / Net Banking OR E Challan Only.

UPSESSB UP TGT Recruitment 2022 Age Limit as on 01/07/2022

  • Minimum Age : 21 Years.
  • Maximum Age : NA
  • Age Relaxation Extra as per Rules.

How to Fill UPSESSB UP TGT 2022 Online Form

  • Uttar Pradesh Madhyamic Shiksha Seva Chayan Board UPMSSB Are Issued Trained Graduate Teacher TGT Recruitment 2022. Notification and Invited Online Application Form for the UP TGT Teacher Post Jobs 2022 Candidate Can Apply Online for 09/06/2022 to 03/07/2022.
  • Candidate Read the Notification Before Apply the UP TGT Latest Teacher Recruitment 2022 Application Form in Sarkari Result Latest Job Section.
  • Kindly Check and Collect the All Document - Hand Writing, Eligibility, ID Proof, Address Details, Basic Details.
  • Kindly Ready Scan Document Related to Recruitment Form - Photo, Sign, ID, Thumb, Proof, Etc.
  • Before Submit the Application Form Must Check the Preview and All Column Carefully.
  • If Candidate Required to Paying the Application Fee Must Submit. If You have Not the Required Application Fees Your Form is Not Completed.
  • Take A Print Out of Final Submitted Form.
